# ZIX - Troubleshooting

## Postfix commands
# show queue
showqueue

# show content of a message
postcat -qv <msgid>

# flush the queue
/zix/system/postfix/bin/postqueue -f -c /zix/system/postfix/conf_base

# zix management interface
zix-cli

# Logs:
/var/log/zixvpm/

